text: Héctor Nemesio Esquiliano Solís (born 31 October 1951) is a Mexican politician from the Institutional Revolutionary Party. He has served as Deputy of the XLIX and LVIII Legislatures of the Mexican Congress representing Quintana Roo. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Quintana Roo Category:People from Chetumal, Quintana Roo Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Institutional Revolutionary Party politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
